{"data":{"post":{"id":"1541d213-b186-533d-8feb-64c462837d7e","html":"<p><figure><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e68835d26fe82d220f7a0d7602e71730/ba646/1210_7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 633px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 85.15007898894156%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1210 7\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/e68835d26fe82d220f7a0d7602e71730/ba646/1210_7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e68835d26fe82d220f7a0d7602e71730/1e307/1210_7.jpg 200w,\n/static/e68835d26fe82d220f7a0d7602e71730/f2b0a/1210_7.jpg 400w,\n/static/e68835d26fe82d220f7a0d7602e71730/ba646/1210_7.jpg 633w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 633px) 100vw, 633px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a><figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">感谢贝贝提供插画”方块鱼”</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>昨天在方案讨论的时发生了冲突，当时我还并未觉察，不知哪个点是导火索？也没有找到哪个细节会激怒他？</p>\n<p>我并不知道哪个行为触发了他的“爆破点”，过后反思：因为认知的差异性导致，在我看来理所当然的事情，却戳破了他的痛点。</p>\n<p>在此反思，再一次拿出《人性的弱点》读书笔记回顾，以下两条：</p>\n<p>第一，尊重别人的意见，使用恰当的方式指出对方的错误；</p>\n<p>第二，从他人的角度出发看问题；</p>\n<p><figure><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0a978e16dd860ec7acaf68f771e73fea/ca978/人性的弱点.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 199.89888776541963%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"     \"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/0a978e16dd860ec7acaf68f771e73fea/48538/人性的弱点.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0a978e16dd860ec7acaf68f771e73fea/bed0f/人性的弱点.png 200w,\n/static/0a978e16dd860ec7acaf68f771e73fea/5fd34/人性的弱点.png 400w,\n/static/0a978e16dd860ec7acaf68f771e73fea/48538/人性的弱点.png 800w,\n/static/0a978e16dd860ec7acaf68f771e73fea/ca978/人性的弱点.png 989w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a><figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">《人性的弱点》读书笔记</figcaption></figure></p>","fields":{"slug":"/2019-01-28/he-was-enraged/","prefix":"2019-01-28"},"frontmatter":{"title":"是什么激怒了对方？","author":"文:Jane","category":"thought","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/e68835d26fe82d220f7a0d7602e71730/ada8c/1210_7.jpg"}}}}},"prev":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019-02-01/reading-painting-books/","prefix":"2019-02-01"},"frontmatter":{"title":"远程互动"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019-01-15/accept-your-imperfections/","prefix":"2019-01-15"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Accept your imperfections"}},"authornote":{"id":"9fe62122-025b-556e-8f79-c5d93f344df9","html":"<p>hustlrb<br>\n<br>\n明德厚学 求是创新</p>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":""}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2019-01-28/he-was-enraged/","total":41,"prev":"/2019-02-01/reading-painting-books/","next":"/2019-01-15/accept-your-imperfections/"}}